				<outline text="Thread from December 2020 warning of a future effort to rehabilitate Bill Barr and lie about what he’s done, which is happening right now https://t.co/HsRRZhG5pG" type="tweet" created="Sun, 27 Jun 2021 13:05:14 GMT" tweetId="1409135736583077894" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1409135736583077894" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
