				<outline text="New @gaslitnation transcript is out! Read the transcript of our latest episode, &quot;Voter Suppression Emergency&quot;, here: https://t.co/6aai0TeKR2 https://t.co/SUC3VZ3JjJ" type="tweet" created="Fri, 25 Jun 2021 20:52:18 GMT" tweetId="1408528499199991814" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1408528499199991814" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
					<outline text="Like getting @gaslitnation transcripts? Join our Patreon! It covers our production costs and keeps our show independent and accessible to all. Plus you get extra episodes, Q &amp;amp; As, more:  https://t.co/Na8D7srDta" type="tweet" created="Fri, 25 Jun 2021 20:54:57 GMT" tweetId="1408529169202307095" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1408529169202307095" inReplyToId="1408528499199991814" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
