				<outline text="The @gaslitnation Biden-Putin Summit Special is out! @AndreaChalupa and I discuss the #GenevaSummit, cybersecurity, the history of Kremlin threats, the lack of consequences for transnational organized crime -- and more! https://t.co/mIRZ5yBCsy" type="tweet" created="Thu, 17 Jun 2021 14:59:12 GMT" tweetId="1405540535549325319" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405540535549325319" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
