			<outline text="June 16" type="calendarDay" name="16" >
				<outline text="@oregontrail https://t.co/RTbcZonfxN" type="tweet" created="Thu, 17 Jun 2021 00:58:14 GMT" tweetId="1405328899807059968" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405328899807059968" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				<outline text="The transcript of last week's @gaslitnation episode, &quot;Red State Resistance&quot; is out! We interview Missouri's @LynzforCongress on how authoritarianism starts at the state level and spreads -- and how to stop it:  https://t.co/7wJJM7Fmt6 https://t.co/wQtJhFVZPp" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 20:12:51 GMT" tweetId="1405257082656497664" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405257082656497664" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				<outline text="Thread on Antony Blinken https://t.co/PrOKEeHnyw" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 14:51:48 GMT" tweetId="1405176287191314432" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405176287191314432" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				<outline text="This tweet is nearly a month old. I got so much harassment for saying it, but it all unfortunately held true, with official confirmation of complicity reported over the past month. https://t.co/QZ8s7USESn" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 14:09:28 GMT" tweetId="1405165633269112833" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405165633269112833" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
					<outline text="Many expressed consternation at the last line. But when I said &quot;Dems won't pass voting rights&quot; I literally meant &quot;Dems won't pass voting rights&quot;, as in the Dem leadership is purposefully refusing to do so! And that is indeed what's been happening: https://t.co/pXWH288pY6" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 14:12:45 GMT" tweetId="1405166459169431553" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405166459169431553" inReplyToId="1405165633269112833" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="&quot;Antony Blinken is in a revolving door of corruption. He should have realized after the Obama admin that global corruption made the US vulnerable. Instead he spent the last few years raking in a massive amount of money from dirty clients.&quot; - @Andreachalupa https://t.co/ne487fJT2H" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 13:40:26 GMT" tweetId="1405158326028079107" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405158326028079107" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
					<outline text="&quot;Because Blinken had so many lucrative contracts, how can we expect he will serve the US public if it jeopardizes his former or future clients? Among these clients are Facebook, Blackstone, Boeing, and other data mining and drone companies...&quot; https://t.co/ne487fJT2H" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 13:44:03 GMT" tweetId="1405159237865644035" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405159237865644035" inReplyToId="1405158326028079107" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
						<outline text="&quot;Blinken family history is troubling. His stepfather Samuel Pisar was the lawyer and very close friend of Robert Maxwell, the Mossad agent/Russian mafia associate who is the father of Ghislaine Maxwell. Pisar was also Jeffrey Epstein's liaison to France.&quot; https://t.co/sSlRzdCwlu" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 13:48:14 GMT" tweetId="1405160290761822214" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405160290761822214" inReplyToId="1405159237865644035" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
						<outline text="&quot;Blinken family history is troubling. His stepfather Samuel Pisar was the lawyer and very close friend of Robert Maxwell, the Mossad agent/Russian mafia associate who is the father of Ghislaine Maxwell. Pisar was also Jeffrey Epstein's liaison to France.&quot; https://t.co/ne487fJT2H" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 13:48:59 GMT" tweetId="1405160479811686402" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405160479811686402" inReplyToId="1405159237865644035" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
							<outline text="&quot;Robert Maxwell kept his mafia and Mossad identities secret from the public, operating as a UK publishing tycoon. It is very unlikely that Pisar did not know the truth given that he recited the kaddish at Maxwell's Israeli state funeral.&quot; -- @gaslitnation https://t.co/ne487fJT2H" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 13:50:26 GMT" tweetId="1405160844451794944" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405160844451794944" inReplyToId="1405160479811686402" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
								<outline text="&quot;There is no indication that Blinken was involved in Maxwell/Epstein activity. He should not be judged by his stepfather, but by his own actions. However, Pisar's extensive ties to international criminal actors make Blinken and the State Dept vulnerable.&quot; https://t.co/ne487fJT2H" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 13:52:13 GMT" tweetId="1405161292219006977" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405161292219006977" inReplyToId="1405160844451794944" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
									<outline text="There's way more where this came from, unfortunately; full @gaslitnation episode here: https://t.co/ne487fJT2H" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 13:53:09 GMT" tweetId="1405161526009401344" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405161526009401344" inReplyToId="1405161292219006977" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
									</outline>
								</outline>
							</outline>
						</outline>
					</outline>
				<outline text="Thread https://t.co/riiy97DCGe" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 13:37:48 GMT" tweetId="1405157663277780998" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405157663277780998" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				<outline text="&quot;The US is not in a position of strength. No country could be when its institutions are hollow or hijacked, purged and packed with criminal lackeys, when people's most basic rights, like the right to vote, are deeply threatened.&quot; -- @gaslitnation https://t.co/ne487fJT2H" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 13:27:00 GMT" tweetId="1405154947319140362" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405154947319140362" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
					<outline text="&quot;It's better to just admit to US flaws. We all can see them. Americans can see them, the world can see them. Hostile foreign actors can see them -- and they can see that the Biden admin isn't fixing them, and that this can be exploited.&quot; -- @gaslitnation https://t.co/ne487fJT2H" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 13:28:56 GMT" tweetId="1405155431492771850" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405155431492771850" inReplyToId="1405154947319140362" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
						<outline text="&quot;The remedy is to fix the flaws -- pass new policies and laws, enforce accountability. This is not just a moral and legal remedy, it's pragmatic protection from foreign threats. Officials cannot cover their eyes. They need to gut out the rot.&quot; https://t.co/ne487fJT2H" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 13:31:50 GMT" tweetId="1405156163994456065" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405156163994456065" inReplyToId="1405155431492771850" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
						</outline>
					</outline>
				<outline text="&quot;The #GenevaSummit is between POTUS and a mass-murdering dictator who is the head of a sweeping criminal mafia state destabilizing the world. When you have that situation, you should ask, 'Who actually won the Cold War?'&quot; - @AndreaChalupa on 
@gaslitnation https://t.co/ne487fJT2H" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 13:00:13 GMT" tweetId="1405148205344604160" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405148205344604160" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
					<outline text="&quot;This is a time to reflect as Americans, as historians. The KGB became the FSB and worked in tandem with bad actors in the West, weaponizing greed and corruption. This whole thing reeks of a hostage situation.&quot; -- @AndreaChalupa on @gaslitnation https://t.co/ne487fJT2H" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 13:01:30 GMT" tweetId="1405148530247876608" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405148530247876608" inReplyToId="1405148205344604160" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
						<outline text="&quot;What the summit signals to Western allies is that Putin is saying 'Everyone has to work with me, because I can get a summit with POTUS.' That hurts Biden's leverage; it shows his tendency to fold.&quot; -- @AndreaChalupa on @gaslitnation https://t.co/ne487fJT2H" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 13:03:41 GMT" tweetId="1405149080150552581" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405149080150552581" inReplyToId="1405148530247876608" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
							<outline text="&quot;Biden's team keep saying they need to have a 'predictable relationship' with Putin, not understanding that Putin's weapon is chaos. He thrives on chaos. He leverages chaos.&quot; -- @AndreaChalupa on @gaslitnation https://t.co/ne487fJT2H" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 13:05:23 GMT" tweetId="1405149506967064576" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405149506967064576" inReplyToId="1405149080150552581" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
							</outline>
						</outline>
					</outline>
				<outline text="&quot;If I were one of our allies, would I believe that the US took the threat of Trump seriously, or autocracy seriously, or transnational organized crime seriously? No, not based on the Biden administration's actions so far.&quot; -- @gaslitnation https://t.co/ne487fJT2H" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 12:49:34 GMT" tweetId="1405145527218475013" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405145527218475013" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
					<outline text="&quot;The refusal to enforce accountability for Trump administration crimes is not just a domestic crisis but a foreign relations crisis. It is a crisis of trust.&quot; -- @gaslitnation https://t.co/ne487fJT2H" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 12:50:30 GMT" tweetId="1405145762628046856" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405145762628046856" inReplyToId="1405145527218475013" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
						<outline text="&quot;What message does it send when a government won’t investigate an attack on its own Capitol by seditionists who are now again announcing their plans for a sequel, unimpeded?&quot; -- @gaslitnation https://t.co/ne487fJT2H" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 12:51:18 GMT" tweetId="1405145962767659018" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405145962767659018" inReplyToId="1405145762628046856" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
							<outline text="&quot;What message does it send when the former president was a known mafia associate who pardoned the criminals who aided him – and those criminals, who are deeply immersed international affairs as well as US affairs, are now roaming free?&quot; --@gaslitnation https://t.co/ne487fJT2H" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 12:52:00 GMT" tweetId="1405146140115353605" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405146140115353605" inReplyToId="1405145962767659018" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
								<outline text="&quot;From 2017 to 2021, Trump and his lackeys treated NATO like a protection racket. They threatened some foreign officials with violence and blackmailed others. They backed the enemies of our allies and the allies of our enemies.&quot; https://t.co/ne487fJT2H" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 12:53:05 GMT" tweetId="1405146413340692482" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405146413340692482" inReplyToId="1405146140115353605" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
									<outline text="&quot;Trump and his crime cult threatened democratic stability in the US in the most blatant of ways...and nearly everyone involved in that crime spree has walked free, with the Biden administration showing not even the *intent* to enforce accountability.&quot; https://t.co/ne487fJT2H" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 12:55:26 GMT" tweetId="1405147001432547331" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1405147001432547331" inReplyToId="1405146413340692482" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
									</outline>
								</outline>
							</outline>
						</outline>
					</outline>
